Interface SQLBatchResultExecutor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JooqDSLProvider
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Jooqx, JooqxBase<S>, JooqxConn, JooqxSession, JooqxTx
    public interface SQLBatchResultExecutor
extends JooqDSLProvider
    The reactive sql executor that is adapted for SqlClient to execute batch SQL command and able to return the number of succeed row and row detail
